videos.description: Carsen Edwards runs a pick-and-roll with Trevion Williams, who dunks it early in the first half for Purdue.
videos.headline: Purdue's Williams flushes dunk off pick-and-roll

videos.description: Minnesota guard Gabe Kalscheur throws a long pass to Amir Coffey upcourt and Coffey powers down the slam.
videos.headline: Minnesota's Coffey dunks in transition

videos.description: Carsen Edwards cuts Minnesota's lead over Purdue with a pull-up 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Edwards pulls up and nails a three in a defender's face

videos.description: Matt Haarms' back-to-back blocks leads to a Carsen Edwards fast-break layup on the other end.
videos.headline: Purdue gets it done on both ends

videos.description: Ryan Cline sinks a big three to give Purdue the lead over Minnesota.
videos.headline: Mackey Complex erupts after Purdue takes the lead
